Product Requirements Document (PRD)
Homeopathy Clinic Management System (HCMS)

A modern, AI-ready clinic management platform for homeopathic clinics with:

Web App (Next.js)
Mobile App (React Native / Flutter recommended)
WhatsApp-first patient communication
Digital patient lifecycle management
In-house medicine billing & inventory
Appointment & follow-up automation
Financial tracking and analytics

Inspired by current clinic-management and EMR trends such as:

WhatsApp appointment/reminder workflows
Digital EMR and patient history systems
Appointment scheduling + online booking
Prescription + billing + reports automation
