Final Recommendation

This is a very strong SaaS opportunity because:

India has massive clinic digitization demand
Homeopathy clinics are underserved
WhatsApp-first workflows are highly valuable in India
Most existing systems are generic and outdated
Clinics need integrated CRM + EMR + billing + communication in one product

The best strategy:

Build for one clinic first
Validate workflows
Convert into multi-tenant SaaS
Add AI + automation later

Recommended initial positioning:

“WhatsApp-first Homeopathy Clinic Operating System for Indian Clinics.”